Rule Name: Chronically Homeless as defined by HUD
Income - Less than 30% Area Median Income (Extremely Low Income)
Income - Less than 50% Area Median Income or less (Very Low Income)
Income - Less than 60% Area Median Income
Income - Less than 80% Area Median Income (Low Income)
Literally homeless as defined by HUD
180 homeless days in past three years
365 homeless days in past three years
